&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join the LTK Family! We are searching for a senior software engineer to join the Creator organization. This team is responsible for the user experiences and systems used to onboard creators and drive their growth across LTK, one of the largest creator-guided shopping and brand marketing platforms in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal Senior Software Engineer for this space will be organized, productive, and comfortable working across the full stack. You will have strong experience in building scalable, production-quality web applications that anticipate significant growth across multiple dimensions. You’ll be inventive and have a pragmatic and iterative approach to delivering high quality software. You’ll ruthlessly prioritize accomplishing the highest impact deliverables first, and provide valuable guidance to the engineering manager on the direction of the team’s web architecture and systems. You will proactively establish lines of communication across the teams and business units, and draw on them to make the team successful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you will make an impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coming up with feasible and practical solutions to tough problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain high-quality fullstack systems and experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take end-to-end ownership of features across the stack: from early technical design and prototyping through implementation, testing, rollout, and ongoing iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product, design, and other engineers to deliver intuitive, performant, and accessible fullstack experiences that delight creators and brands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize fullstack applications and services for performance, scalability, and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion best practices in architecture, usability, security, and cross-platform compatibility across the full stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools to expedite daily workflows (e.g., code generation, refactoring, test creation, documentation) and to improve both speed and quality of web development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI-assisted development practices to prototype, iterate on, and maintain web features efficiently, while holding a high bar for safety and code quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write very high-quality, well-tested code that is robust and easy to maintain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ownership of projects and drive them to completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work and succeed in a fast-paced and agile development environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and drive improvements to our fullstack architecture, tooling, and development processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct constructive peer design/code reviews and provide clear, actionable feedback.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with distributed teams across different time zones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a technical subject matter expert for fullstack development who mentors fellow engineers, demonstrates technical experience, and leads teams in solving challenging problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
